# Project State - <REPLACE: project name>

This file maps the current research state before a workstream chooses a state
object and gate. The project container can contain multiple workstreams; the
workstream is the unit that selects a local protocol such as Capability /
Technology Research or Phenomenon / Mechanism Research.

